  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment (MRL 3)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. This package re-evaluates COU1 at Model Risk Level 3 following an expanded regulatory scope requiring higher model influence weighting. Seven factors are fully assessed and meet required levels; three factors are recorded as not-assessed on the basis that they fall 'beyond the scope of the current submission phase', without concrete supporting justification. At MRL 3 this constitutes a material credibility gap.",
