    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-cardiovascular-modeling-group",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team determined that the seven assessed factors collectively meet or exceed their required levels at MRL 3, and that the three unassessed factors (Numerical solver error, Use error, Equivalency of input parameters) are considered beyond the scope of the current submission phase. The team concluded that prior experience with this pump class and the quality of the assessed factors provide sufficient overall credibility for the COU decision. The package is accepted at Medium assurance level. Note: no formal documented justification for deferral of unassessed factors at MRL 3 has been provided; this represents an unmitigated credibility gap.",
